examples.en: The police have been observing his movements.
The class will be observing the movements of fish.
Children learn by observing their parents and others.
He wasted his eyes in observing the stars.
His care in observing the rules of good health amounted to a kind of religiousness.
Researchers are observing the course of the disease at the cellular level.
My piano teacher often reproves me for slouching while playing, observing that good posture helps one play better.
